Package: TreeAngle
Type: Package
Title: Geometric Statistic for Spatial-Temporal Association in Cell Lineage Trees
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person(given = "Shanjun", family = "Mao", email = "shjmao@hnu.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person(given = "Xiaodan", family = "Fan", role = "aut"),
      person(given = "Jie", family = "Hu", role = "aut"),
      person(given = "Sixuan", family = "Liu", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Computes the geometric TreeAngle statistic for paired generation-structured
    data, with optional normalization following the TDDeltaTheta algorithm.
    The package accepts generation-wise list input, matrices or data frames
    with a generation column, or direct two-column paired data. It also provides
    simulation utilities for manuscript-style synthetic data generation.
